data.description: Fantastic home in the Hidden Oaks Subdivision located on entrance to Cul de sac, perfect for kids to play outdoors. This home offers a privacy fenced yard, split floor plan, granite countertops, kitchen island, tray ceilings, recessed lighting throughout. Don't miss the chance to make this charming home your own, it's ready for your personal touch! Schedule a viewing today!
